                    <p class="mb-1 font-['Sora'] text-sm font-semibold text-slate-950">Editor family</p>
                    <p class="mb-0 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">
                        Browse every editor product:
                        <a class="font-semibold text-slate-900 no-underline transition hover:text-cyan-600" href="https://richtextbox.com">RichTextBox</a>
                        for ASP.NET Core,
